## Edge Cases
- If a source returns HTTP 402, 401, or redirects to a login page, treat as paywall regardless of body content.
- If extracted body is empty (0 words), log as `insufficient_content` and count toward paywall rate only if a paywall pattern was detected in the raw HTML.
