### Step 1: Per-Source Daily Cap (Max 3 Articles Per Source)

After scoring, group articles by `source_id` and enforce a cap of 3 per source per day:

```typescript
function applyPerSourceCap(articles: Article[], capPerSource: number = 3): Article[] {
  const sourceCount: Record<string, number> = {};
  return articles
    .sort((a, b) => b.composite_score - a.composite_score) // keep highest-scoring per source
    .filter(article => {
      const sid = article.source_id;
      if (!sourceCount[sid]) sourceCount[sid] = 0;
      if (sourceCount[sid] < capPerSource) {
        sourceCount[sid]++;
        return true;
      }
      return false;
    });
}
```

Call this after scoring and before threshold filtering.

