## Step 1: Database Schema Changes

Add two new columns to the `newsletters` table (or a dedicated `stat_of_the_day` table if one exists):

```sql
ALTER TABLE newsletters
  ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS stat_source_article_id uuid REFERENCES articles(id),
  ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS stat_validation_notes text;
```

- `stat_source_article_id`: Foreign key to the `articles` table row from which the stat was extracted.
- `stat_validation_notes`: Free-text field storing the result of any web-search verification step (search query used, result snippet, confidence assessment, or a note that no verification was needed/possible).

