## Considerations

- Pass full article objects (including `content` or `summary` fields) to `generateStatOfTheDay`, not just titles, so Claude has enough text to extract a real stat.
- Ensure `stat_source_article_id` is validated against the actual article IDs in the current pipeline run to prevent hallucinated UUIDs.
- The web search is rate-limited and should only fire for numeric stats to minimize API costs.
- Log a warning (and optionally notify admin via Task 38's notification system) when no stat is found so the omission is observable.
